text: TeleXitos is an American Spanish language television network owned by NBCUniversal Telemundo Enterprises. Aimed at the Hispanic and Latin American community, the network airs a mix of dramatic television series from the 1970s to the 2000s and movies. All programming is dubbed into Spanish. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Companies based in New York City Category:2012 establishments in the United States Category:American television networks
